Class GlobalSimilarityRegistry

java.lang.Object
  jcolibri.cbrcore.GlobalSimilarityRegistry

public class GlobalSimilarityRegistry
extends java.lang.Object

Registry of the managers of the package global similarities. It is implemented using the Singleton pattern.

Author:
Antonio A. Sánchez Ruiz-Granados
